{"title":"唐僧肉大家解馋","authors":["池北偶张滨"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":4,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐僧肉大家解馋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗张滨画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴建基础设施，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家拨出巨款。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到唐僧肥肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都要咬口解馋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大笔建设资金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层层截留挤占，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挪用已经成风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动辄百万千万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或盖办公大楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或建豪华宾馆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或造花园别墅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或买汽车房产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑路可以放慢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修堤不妨从缓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官员得其所哉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百姓只能瞪眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"损害国家利益，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂能听任不管。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此违法乱纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定要认真查办。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}